// `bslstl::StopStateCallbackNode` classes, which are for internal use only
// and are used to implement `bsl::stop_source`, `bsl::stop_token`, and
// `bsl::stop_callback`.  Please include `<bsl_stop_token.h>` instead.
//
///Usage
